private theorem Lemma7 (ПҒ : MState (H i)) {Оө : Prob} (hОө : 0 < Оө вҲ§ Оө < 1) (Пғ : (n : в„•) вҶ’ IsFree (i := i ^ n)) :
    (R2 ПҒ Пғ вүҘ R1 ПҒ Оө) вҶ’
    вҲҖ Оө' : Prob, (hОө' : 0 < Оө' вҲ§ Оө' < Оө) вҶ’ -- Оө' is written as \tilde{Оө} in the paper.
    вҲғ Пғ' : (n : в„•) вҶ’ IsFree (i := i ^ n),
    R2 ПҒ Пғ' - R1 ПҒ Оө вүӨ .ofNNReal (1 - Оө' : Prob) * (R2 ПҒ Пғ - R1 ПҒ Оө)
    := by
  --This proof naturally splits out into LemmaS62:
  --  `lim inf nвҶ’вҲһ 1/n D(E_n(ПҒ^вҠ—n)вҖ–Пғ''_n) вҲ’ R1,Пө вүӨ (1 вҲ’ ЛңПө)(R2 вҲ’ R1,Пө).`
  --This is proved in appendix C.
  --Then we prove S61, and the conclusion is just `rw [S61] at S62`. But splitting it like
  --this requires first _defining_ the sequence Пғ''_n.

  --First deal with the easy case of R1 = R2.
  intro hR1R2 Оө' вҹЁhОө'вӮҒ, hОө'вӮӮвҹ©
  rw [ge_iff_le, le_iff_lt_or_eq, or_comm] at hR1R2
  rcases hR1R2 with hR1R2|hR1R2
